Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了  是泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.01,0:01:37.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈看起來好像很高興呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.95,0:01:42.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為她第一次來遊樂園的游泳池嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.24,0:01:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  為什麼這麼多女生就結城君一個男生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:50.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我帶來的  不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不是不可以…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.89,0:01:55.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,王子要看好公主的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.71,0:01:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.05,0:01:58.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少囉唆
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.71,0:02:19.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  小春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.85,0:02:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗也過來啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.08,0:02:27.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.04,0:02:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水槍砰砰water君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.00,0:02:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.92,0:02:41.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直為了讓你關注我而努力到現在
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.43,0:02:47.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時我想讓你高興…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.88,0:02:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君  你還好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:03:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我擔心你…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:02.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.23,0:03:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有時候我想要治癒你  就努力…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.48,0:03:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.10,0:03:18.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.26,0:03:28.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明都這麼拚命地努力了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.51,0:03:31.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你卻連看都不看我一眼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.12,0:03:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}知道什麼叫跟蹤狂嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.71,0:03:36.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天我一定要…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.01,0:03:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.27,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  我想成為梨斗君的第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.57,0:03:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該說  我想做你的妻子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一定要讓你…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關注起我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:13.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  要去咯  接著
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,春菜  去你那邊咯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.28,0:04:30.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君  對不起  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.40,0:04:37.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小春菜  居然離我這麼近
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.73,0:04:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.34,0:04:52.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  小倫  我還以為是奇怪的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.78,0:04:54.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.89,0:05:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在是機會
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊  小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.77,0:05:14.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  軟膏增乳劑
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.43,0:05:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的玩法…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.65,0:05:17.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.61,0:05:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這變態！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.67,0:05:26.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.38,0:05:35.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.26,0:05:44.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城梨斗  你不要忘記我一直在伺機殺你
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.89,0:05:49.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  你居然敢故意氣我  膽子真不小
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.28,0:06:01.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手  求你停下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.69,0:06:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好慘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.66,0:06:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  泳池裡好像沒有波浪呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.45,0:06:11.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為畢竟不是海嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:14.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然也有那種有波浪  還會流動的泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.81,0:06:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的泳池好像是沒有的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.15,0:06:19.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此  就只有捨身突擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.73,0:06:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.17,0:06:24.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.26,0:06:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.16,0:06:32.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.98,0:06:35.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  這是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.04,0:06:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新發明  潑潑波浪君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.41,0:06:39.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起玩漂流好舒服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.70,0:06:41.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.33,0:06:59.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.84,0:07:06.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗和小倫  好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.14,0:07:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是厲不厲害的問題
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.79,0:07:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君  沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.35,0:07:21.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君  對不起  都怪我抱著你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.50,0:07:22.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.68,0:07:26.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然這樣說  不過真是拿她沒辦法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.97,0:07:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會看情況的水平真是可以跟菈菈有得一拼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:33.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去對面稍微休息下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.10,0:07:34.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.96,0:07:37.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  你要去哪裡啊  等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.01,0:07:38.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.07,0:07:41.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  我們也去吃午飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生這麼多事  也累了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.43,0:07:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.30,0:07:45.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.90,0:07:53.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊  為什麼大家都妨礙我和梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.05,0:07:57.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會是大家  都對梨斗君有意思吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.15,0:08:00.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.48,0:08:07.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  我一定要贏  然後搶走梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.22,0:08:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我絕對不會把梨斗君交給你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.02,0:08:21.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要和梨斗君獨處的話
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.52,0:08:23.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就必須要排除那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在梨斗君面前讓她們出醜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.33,0:08:30.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她們再也不好意思出現
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.49,0:08:37.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這個搶走她們的泳衣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.82,0:08:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓她們變得見不得人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:49.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上鉤了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.60,0:08:52.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.33,0:08:57.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家來比賽吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.50,0:08:59.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,準備  開始
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.40,0:09:13.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇  好高啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.39,0:09:15.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我先下去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.27,0:09:18.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.38,0:09:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛  要脫落了  要脫落了  要脫落了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.24,0:09:29.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.80,0:09:34.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君  你好像沒什麼精神啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  沒這回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.85,0:09:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然如此只好使用必殺招了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.16,0:09:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就用這個非常好用  只吃泳衣的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:48.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天然宇宙食人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.82,0:09:50.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.61,0:09:53.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  有魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.07,0:09:54.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.03,0:09:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.13,0:09:59.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  泳池裡有魚是不是有點奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.04,0:10:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些魚怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.99,0:10:08.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好色的魚!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈大人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.18,0:10:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個好像是宇宙食人魚
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.76,0:10:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙食人魚？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.14,0:10:16.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不會咬人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.83,0:10:20.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過纖維的東西它們都很喜歡  泳衣會被吃掉的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.04,0:10:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  這種時候就要…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.59,0:10:29.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,織織網絲君  金屬鋼絲版
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.55,0:10:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.66,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊有個貌似頭目的大傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.45,0:10:42.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:52.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.54,0:11:04.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.34,0:11:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.50,0:11:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.23,0:11:24.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  都是小倫搞的鬼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.04,0:11:27.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.53,0:11:30.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你為什麼要做那種事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.49,0:11:32.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:36.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…梨斗君…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.28,0:11:36.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.95,0:11:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.93,0:11:40.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做什麼了 結城
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.27,0:11:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  我什麼都沒做
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.06,0:11:46.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冤枉啊  跟我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.04,0:11:49.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你居然…梨斗君…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.58,0:11:53.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.62,0:11:54.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.72,0:11:55.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.95,0:11:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不用對她那麼凶吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.25,0:12:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.59,0:12:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們看好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.11,0:12:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我展現下我夏日的搭訕技術
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.28,0:12:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是弄光學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.89,0:12:12.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實在是夏之男的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.12,0:12:18.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我發現了一個正在傷心的好女人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.09,0:12:21.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有可以讓我搭訕的資格
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.58,0:12:23.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是弄光學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.44,0:12:25.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超高傲的口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.28,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打正在傷心的女孩的主意  真精明
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.38,0:12:36.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  如果有想要的東西  我弄光都會買給你的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.25,0:12:40.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  只要你和我玩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.17,0:12:42.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是弄光學長
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.00,0:12:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接誘發她的物質需求
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.31,0:12:49.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是二十年前的搭訕方法了  但是太古老也有新意啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.60,0:12:56.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂  你去哪裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.24,0:13:00.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰淇淋十個  哈密瓜汽水二十杯  法蘭克熱狗二十根
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.93,0:13:03.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕎麥麵三十份  咖喱三十份  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.22,0:13:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是最近流行起來的暴食女孩嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.73,0:13:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒也不討厭…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.28,0:13:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是學長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.67,0:13:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對流行也很敏感啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.01,0:13:26.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問  是一起的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.25,0:13:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.90,0:13:30.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一共48500元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.61,0:13:32.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.35,0:13:34.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  找您1500元
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.65,0:13:35.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是學長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.05,0:13:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真慷慨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.43,0:13:39.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  你該和我…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.05,0:13:40.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.89,0:13:43.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是學長
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.19,0:13:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這客請得讓人佩服
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即使暴飲暴食了也不能讓心情好起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.64,0:13:53.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被梨斗君那麼說了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.85,0:13:56.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連活下去的勇氣都沒有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.22,0:14:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我一點關係都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.77,0:14:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別再對我糾纏不清了  你這發情期的雌猩猩
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.45,0:14:08.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs20}沒有講過這樣的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.40,0:14:13.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後要怎麼活下去啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.20,0:14:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.00,0:14:21.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝大家捧場
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.78,0:14:25.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  要成為名人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.37,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成為名人  站在梨斗君高不可攀的位置
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.43,0:14:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來  梨斗君就…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.09,0:14:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:51.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倫小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.54,0:15:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近的偶像不怎麼樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.61,0:15:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼說呢  沒什麼個性
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.23,0:15:14.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然偶像還是集中在80年代
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.85,0:15:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佐多原喜和子  勝也津由里  都神插繪  波塔茲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.62,0:15:21.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起打擾了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.46,0:15:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.59,0:15:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您那銳利的目光看透那位出不了頭的偶像的能力
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.06,0:15:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想您應該是一位著名的老師
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:35.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的確…是老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.18,0:15:37.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是老師嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是…雖說是老師…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請把我  請把我培養成為一流的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.06,0:15:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.84,0:15:54.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此這般我開始了為成為偶像而刻苦訓練的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.10,0:15:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼老師  請多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.07,0:16:02.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你又擅自把我帶到這種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.07,0:16:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣  老師
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.19,0:16:11.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.69,0:16:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.63,0:16:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這回是哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.00,0:16:21.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師  我想唱歌還是要學腹式呼吸的對嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.63,0:16:23.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也這麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.35,0:16:25.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個我也不是很懂
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:28.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是要自己考慮的吧  我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.01,0:16:40.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  訓練是異常艱辛的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.21,0:16:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做不到  無論怎麼努力都跳不好阿拉伯風格的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.71,0:16:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  差不多該回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.69,0:16:54.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣  是說像我這樣愚笨不機靈的烏龜只好回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.54,0:16:58.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我放棄成為偶像嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.28,0:17:02.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想回自己的家裡去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.14,0:17:04.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.58,0:17:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像我這種沒有才能的人  只有獻出身體
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.25,0:17:11.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.71,0:17:17.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果  女子屈從於權勢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.74,0:17:20.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,經紀公司也好  有名的作曲家也好
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.14,0:17:23.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果沒看中你就沒有前途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.86,0:17:27.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣  我才能加入80年代的偶像行列中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.78,0:17:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  老師  我還沒做好心理準備
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.49,0:17:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你  也差不多該回去了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.08,0:17:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西連寺
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:48.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫會去哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.06,0:17:53.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫  也許喜歡結城君吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.81,0:17:57.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？  這…這不知道呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.70,0:18:04.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想被喜歡的人說了嚴厲的話  對女孩子的打擊非常大
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟我沒關係
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.82,0:18:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算說的人不經意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.21,0:18:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是我的話  還是會很傷心  也許會哭出來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.47,0:18:24.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  去找小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.46,0:18:38.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管怎麼等待  始終沒有一步登天的機會
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.34,0:18:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,工作也一直是作為男人慾望的發洩對像
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.26,0:18:46.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歸根到底  我就是那種程度的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師也拋棄了我
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.35,0:18:59.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人總是先讓女人看到夢想  再和她們擦肩而過
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.44,0:19:01.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫我去買冰淇淋汽水好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.43,0:19:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像這樣  下一個男人又循環而至
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.22,0:19:14.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪裡了  小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.15,0:19:20.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  這只是哈密瓜汽水
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.69,0:19:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個冰塊都沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.52,0:19:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的事已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.93,0:19:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  男人一開始會用溫柔的聲音和你打招呼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.73,0:19:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最後卻會對你施暴
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.85,0:19:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次愛上的那個人也是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.42,0:19:43.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了  你這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.57,0:19:53.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫  你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.57,0:19:54.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.72,0:19:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來  回到大家那裡去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.68,0:19:58.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.44,0:20:02.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼隨隨便便就想把人帶走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.61,0:20:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫是我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.75,0:20:06.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這小鬼說什麼鬼話
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.91,0:20:09.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:11.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結城君  小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.87,0:20:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然叫警察了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.95,0:20:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.88,0:20:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.23,0:20:19.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.07,0:20:20.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們想怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.73,0:20:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那邊的黑眼鏡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.10,0:20:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧  砰砰water君的真正力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.66,0:20:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.99,0:20:41.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.63,0:20:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是因為梨斗和小倫都是我的朋友啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.28,0:20:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幫你是理所應當的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.28,0:20:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.94,0:20:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.78,0:20:58.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗  你沒事真是太好啦  梨斗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.39,0:21:00.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,靠太近啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  放開我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.62,0:21:08.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗君  謝謝你救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.73,0:21:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天真是對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.33,0:21:15.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是  是我說話太過分了  對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.66,0:21:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菈菈  也謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.67,0:21:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了好了  都是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:23.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是結城能為了女孩挺身而出呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.78,0:21:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挺能幹啊  對吧  春菜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.06,0:21:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯…對啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.60,0:21:31.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,梨斗很靠得住吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:35.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不是靠得住還不知道  不過稍微有點刮目相看了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…什麼嘛…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.29,0:21:40.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.88,0:21:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去咯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.46,0:21:43.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不餓嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.05,0:21:44.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好餓啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.98,0:21:47.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那吃點東西再回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.19,0:21:49.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小倫  怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.19,0:21:52.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是很好的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.06,0:21:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.49,0:22:00.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的戀愛戰鬥才剛開始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過  我不會輸的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.79,0:23:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,據說我們高中的舊校舍會出現那個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.73,0:23:44.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  是指什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.69,0:23:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個就是那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.23,0:23:47.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到了夏天就會出現的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.37,0:23:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰巧克力？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.13,0:23:49.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.22,0:23:49.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,透明的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.01,0:23:50.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  水母
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.91,0:23:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是有生命的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.39,0:23:53.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有腳的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.07,0:23:53.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,折椅？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.60,0:23:55.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,音樂教室裡的肖像畫正在看這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.90,0:23:57.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自動追蹤系統？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.22,0:23:59.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明沒人  卻有鋼琴的聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.39,0:24:00.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幻聽?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.29,0:24:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且  理科室的人體模型動起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.54,0:24:05.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太難了  不知道啊
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.85,0:24:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集  To  LOVEる
Dialogue: 0,0:24:07.07,0:24:08.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舊校舍的幽靈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:09.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  不小心回答了
